node.text:
LINK IN BIO. Quantum entanglement is a quantum mechanical phenomenon in which the quantum states of two or more objects have to be described with reference to each other, even though the individual objects may be spatially separated. This leads to correlations between observable physical properties of the systems.

#4BIDDENKNOWLEDGE #billycarsonofficial #billycarson
